Package: spLag
Type: Package
Title: spLag: generate spatio-temporal lags
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-07-05
Author: Katrin Paula
Maintainer: Katrin Paula <Katrin.Paula@uni-mannheim.de>
Description: The spLag package generates spatio-temporal lags based on different spatial weights matrices. The package allows to define different operationalisations of a spatial weights matrix (e.g. decay functions, inverting, row-standardization, bounded matrices) from a  simple distance matrix and to create spatio-temporal lags for longitudinal datasets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE


